Please change parameters configuration in gateway.conf file to your proyect requirements

Devices indicates the MAC number device of the devices that are being conected 
(you can add more devices writin deviceN = MAC, where N in device is one number for each device existing in your network connecting to the gateway via BLE)

Broker_address is the ip your broker is located inside your local network
broker_port is the port you are using to connect to your broker (standar MQTT is 1883)
topic is the topic you are deciding to link your MQTT message (write "#" if you don't need or want a topic)

user and pasword are your credentials when you DO NOT allow anonimous users to connect (if you want to allow anonimous
users to read and write to and from your broker check line 76)




